  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485920/extras/745cf6ba18c6e5efe37c317aecb6e2c8.webp?t=1682178238\" width=600 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Neon Warp is a simple yet very unique puzzle game.</strong></h2> <br>On each level there are blocks of 3 colors. When you move the frame from a block of one color to a block of another a third color appears. <br><br>Using this technique your goal is to repaint all blocks into a single color and you need to do it with least amount of turns.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>150 levels</strong><br></li><li><strong>Time trial mode with 10+ levels</strong><br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Steam achievements and leaderboards</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485920/extras/745cf6ba18c6e5efe37c317aecb6e2c8.webp?t=1682178238\" width=600 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Neon Warp is a simple yet very unique puzzle game.</strong></h2> <br>On each level there are blocks of 3 colors. When you move the frame from a block of one color to a block of another a third color appears. <br><br>Using this technique your goal is to repaint all blocks into a single color and you need to do it with least amount of turns.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>150 levels</strong><br></li><li><strong>Time trial mode with 10+ levels</strong><br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Steam achievements and leaderboards</li></ul>",
